    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chests of drawers having seven drawers and intended to hold a week's supply of clothing; of a type originally made in 18th-century France, Italy, and elsewhere.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
